api

Class EquityTradeResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • api.EquityTradeResponse
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    TdaEquityTradeResponse

    public class EquityTradeResponse
extends Object
    The response from an EquityTradeRequest.

    The most important thing about the EquityTradeResponse is the mapping between the local TRDR client ID and the broker order ID for future AccountActivity updates.

    Author:
    Kyle
